        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You use the power of nightmares to magically replicate the venomous attack of the aberrant and cunning Leng spiders. You deal [[/r 2d6 #piercing]] piercing damage to the touched creature and afflict it with Leng spider venom. If the target takes piercing damage, they must attempt a Fortitude save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes [[/r 2d6 #poison]] poison damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is afflicted with Leng Spider Venom at stage 1.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is afflicted with Leng spider venom at stage 2.</p><hr /><p><b>Leng Spider Venom</b> (incapacitation, poison) <b>Level 13</b></p><p><b>Maximum Duration</b> 6 rounds</p><p><b>Stage 1</b> [[/r 2d6 #poison]] poison damage and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1} (1 round)</p><p><b>Stage 2</b> [[/r 3d6 #poison]] poison damage and Drained 2 (1 round)</p><p><b>Stage 3</b> [[/r 4d6 #poison]] poison damage, Drained 2, and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Confused]{Confused} (1 round)</p>"
